# Space Law Corpus — .gitignore
# We deliberately keep this list SHORT. The corpus is meant to be self-contained
# and durable, so most artifacts (including original source files) are tracked,
# not ignored. Only transient/local junk is excluded.

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# Python tooling (scripts/)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.env

# Local scratch
scratch/
*.tmp
*.log

# NOTE: We do NOT ignore PDFs or other source artifacts. Storing originals
# byte-for-byte is a provenance requirement (see docs/design/01 and 04).
# If large binaries become an issue, we adopt Git LFS rather than ignoring them.
